snippet.title: Announcement Teaser Trailer | Warhammer 40,000: Rogue Trader
snippet.description:
Owlcat is proud to announce the first classic cRPG in the Warhammer 40,000 Universe!
Preorder now -  https://roguetrader.owlcat.games
Take the mantle of a Rogue Trader and explore the vast and dangerous Koronus Expanse with a crew of your loyal companions.

Follow our official media to stay up-to-date with any and all news:
Official site: https://owlcat.games/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/owlcatgames
Discord: https://discord.gg/owlcat
